  "original_title": "Young man dies after falling off waterfall",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Young man dies after falling off waterfall",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A youth had died after falling near a waterfall at the Sun Valley estate in Udaweriya, Haldummulla, after he had attempted to take a photograph near the waterfall.",
        "The police said that the deceased as heen identified as a 24-year-old resident of Welamitiyawa, \u00a0Guruthalawa.",
        "The victim had visited the waterfall with another person on Saturday (4), where he attempted to take a picture near the waterfall, however he had missed his step and fallen off.",
        "Later, during a joint search operation conducted by the police and local residents, the police said that the body was found in a waterhole about 200 meters below the site of the incident.",
        "If IMF reforms not implemented, Sri Lanka goes back to square one \u2013 CBSL Chief"
      ],
